Star - Class in com.googlecode.starrating
A label acting as a half of a star
Depending on its Star.index and Star.starEnabled the left/right or enabled/disabled image is used
The default stars size is 8x20
A StarMouseAdapter for receiving mouse events
StarRating - Class in com.googlecode.starrating
StarRating Class StarRating is a JPanel that holds images of half stars The rate ranges from 0 to the number of stars with a step of 0.5.
